channel.title: ! My Gallery Of Graphics. (39 And Counting!)
channel.description:
Okay, i'm bored, so i'll post all of my ps work since...i don't know. It will be from newest to oldest, and i might not post some of them if im ashemed :rolleyes:. Anyway, i'm updating every 5 sigs, so there is somthing to look at :D.
And also, i have done pictures for other people....[size=12pt]pm me if you want one..[/size] I'm .Genesis now, and my work says Kaza, so for future refrence, [b]I'm Kaza[/b]. Mmmk?

item.description:
@kaza wrote:

Brush your back ground,

Then go Image > apply > image

Then go > Filters > Blur > Gaussian blur > 3.0 > Set it to lighten.

Add render, text, border, done.
